OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778760670
OL,3,C'Life-changing' SMA treatments for
OL,4,Cchildren to be rolled out on NHS
OL,6,FHundreds of children with a rare
OL,7,Fmuscle-wasting condition are set to
OL,8,Freceive access to two "life-changing"
OL,9,Ftreatments after they were approved
OL,10,Ffor widespread use on the NHS.
OL,12,FNHS England will make two treatments
OL,13,Ffor spinal muscular atrophy (SMA)
OL,14,Froutinely available following approval
OL,15,Fby the National Institute for Health
OL,16,Fand Care Excellence (NICE).
OL,18,FA commercial agreement has also been
OL,19,Freached, giving all eligible patients
OL,20,Flifelong access to nusinersen and
OL,21,Frisdiplam on the NHS.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778760670
OL,3,C'Life-changing' SMA treatments for
OL,4,Cchildren to be rolled out on NHS
OL,6,FNusinersen is given as a regular
OL,7,Finjection into the spinal fluid, while
OL,8,Frisdiplam is taken as a daily syrup or
OL,9,Ftablet at home.
OL,11,FA mother whose son received one of the
OL,12,Ftreatments through an early access
OL,13,Fscheme said it had "fundamentally
OL,14,Fchanged the course of his life."
OL,16,FNHS England found the treatments
OL,17,Fhelped 73 children with the most
OL,18,Fsevere form of SMA - Type 1 - survive
OL,19,Fto age five or older, more than half
OL,20,Fof those treated.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778760670
OL,3,C'Life-changing' SMA treatments for
OL,4,Cchildren to be rolled out on NHS
OL,6,FIn its final guidance, NICE said the
OL,7,Fdrugs can improve survival, slow
OL,8,Fdisease progression and help patients
OL,9,Fmaintain their independence.
OL,11,FWhat is SMA?
OL,13,FSpinal muscular atrophy is a rare
OL,14,Fgenetic condition that causes
OL,15,Fprogressive muscle weakness, according
OL,16,Fto the NHS.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778760670
OL,3,C'Life-changing' SMA treatments for
OL,4,Cchildren to be rolled out on NHS
OL,6,FWithout treatment, it can lead to
OL,7,Fsevere disability and reduced life
OL,8,Fexpectancy. Babies with the most
OL,9,Fserious form of the disease are not
OL,10,Fexpected to live beyond two years.
OL,12,FAround 70 babies are estimated to be
OL,13,Fborn with the condition each year in
OL,14,Fthe UK.
OL,16,FSMA is typically grouped into types
OL,17,Fbased on the age at which symptoms
OL,18,Ffirst appear and how they affect
OL,19,Fmovement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
