PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778760670
OL,3,C'Life-changing' SMA treatments for
OL,4,Cchildren to be rolled out on NHS
OL,6,FAround 1,150 people in England are
OL,7,Fliving with types one, two or three of
OL,8,Fthe condition, the NHS said.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
