PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778760670
OL,3,C'Life-changing' SMA treatments for
OL,4,Cchildren to be rolled out on NHS
OL,6,FProfessor James Palmer, national
OL,7,Fmedical director for specialised
OL,8,Fservices at NHS England, said: "These
OL,9,Flifeline treatments have offered a
OL,10,Fphenomenal step forward in care for
OL,11,Fchildren and families affected by such
OL,12,Fa debilitating condition, and it is
OL,13,Ffantastic that they will now be
OL,14,Favailable on the NHS in the long-term.
OL,26,@pD@`OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
