PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778760670
OL,3,C'Life-changing' SMA treatments for
OL,4,Cchildren to be rolled out on NHS
OL,6,F"For parents who faced the
OL,7,Funimaginable pain of thinking their
OL,8,Fchild would not reach their second
OL,9,Fbirthday, they now have hope of seeing
OL,10,Fthem walk to school and play with
OL,11,Ftheir friends, thanks to these life-
OL,12,Fchanging new therapies on the NHS."
OL,14,FEzra Thorman, now nine, started
OL,15,Ftreatment with nusinersen when he was
OL,16,Ffive months old through an NHS access
OL,17,Fprogramme.
OL,19,FHe was diagnosed with SMA Type 1 in
OL,20,F2016 and is now in year 4 at school in
OL,21,FRamsgate, Kent.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778760670
OL,3,C'Life-changing' SMA treatments for
OL,4,Cchildren to be rolled out on NHS
OL,6,FHis mother, Portia Thorman, said:
OL,7,F"Starting mainstream school is a
OL,8,Fmilestone we were once told Ezra would
OL,9,Fnever reach.
OL,11,F"His SMA Type 1 diagnosis in 2016 came
OL,12,Fwith a life expectancy of under two-
OL,13,Fyears-old.
OL,15,F"The hope for a future this bright
OL,16,Ffelt out of reach, however accessing
OL,17,Ftreatment at just five months old
OL,18,Ffundamentally changed the course of
OL,19,Fhis life."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
