PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778760670
OL,3,C'Life-changing' SMA treatments for
OL,4,Cchildren to be rolled out on NHS
OL,6,FThe condition gained national
OL,7,Fprominence after pop star Jesy Nelson
OL,8,Fbegan campaigning for routine
OL,9,Fscreening after her newborn twins were
OL,10,Fdiagnosed with the condition.
OL,12,FNelson has since dedicated herself to
OL,13,Fraising awareness of SMA and has urged
OL,14,Fthe government to add it to the
OL,15,Fnewborn blood spot screening test,
OL,16,Farguing that early treatment can help
OL,17,Fprevent some of its most devastating
OL,18,Feffects.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
