FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778760670
OL,3,C'Life-changing' SMA treatments for
OL,4,Cchildren to be rolled out on NHS
OL,6,FHelen Knight, director of medicines
OL,7,Fevaluation at Nice, said: "After
OL,8,Fcarefully reviewing the latest
OL,9,Fevidence and real-world experience
OL,10,Ffrom the NHS, our independent
OL,11,Fcommittee concluded that nusinersen
OL,12,Fand risdiplam can offer substantial,
OL,13,Flife-changing benefits for many people
OL,14,Fwith SMA.
OL,16,F"These treatments can help people live
OL,17,Flonger, maintain their independence,
OL,18,Fcommunication and participation in
OL,19,Feveryday life, and reduce the need for
OL,20,Fhospital care."
OL,26,@oD@[OUxD@AOU|D@OO]
